description:
IMPORTANT NOTICE:

Hello everyone! Lately in the comments I have often seen people complaining that my LoRA are similar to each other or are not representative of the style they should represent. My models are not trained on material from other artists, and it is therefore difficult to explain what the actual output should be. Since preparing the material necessary for the publication of a LoRA usually takes me a day's work, I have therefore decided not to post all my LoRAs on CivitAI anymore, but from today I will only post those that I consider interesting enough for the audience of this site. If you are interested in downloading the other LoRA as well, you will find them all for FREE (and they'll always be) on my Patreon page (subscribers will have early access to each of these). Thank you all for your support!

I've started a community on Deviant Art to share images made with my models/LoRAs! Join here if you are interested!

IF YOU ARE NEW TO STABLE DIFFUSION OR YOU HAVE PROBLEMS WITH MY MODELS, GO HERE: Guide

IF YOUR PICTURES HAVE PROBLEMS, CHECK MY FAQ SECTION: FAQs

What's new in V2?

V2 is improved in every way possible. It has been trained on a larger, fine-tuned dataset, with more diverse poses and colors. Can easily do SFW and NSFW and has a way more consistent style.

What's this LoRA

This is a LoRA trained on a particular style. It creates illustrations with a vintage Disney cartoon style. It is also available as a checkpoint here: https://civitai.com/models/33707/mistoonamethyst

The images in the examples (v2) are created using only this LoRA and my Mistoon_Sapphire model:

  • https://civitai.com/models/32022

You don't need to specify a word to trigger this LoRA.

The LoRA works also on NSFW (check last examples).

The images are created using different weights (you can check on the image generation panel)

Guides

Learn how to create pictures like mine with my step-by-step tutorials:

  • Beginner's Guide

  • Prompting

  • High Resolution

  • Inpainting

  • ControlNet

  • My Workflow

If you want to create images with a high LoRA weight, I highly suggest you to check the tutorial.

Support My Work

Check out my Patreon for exclusive content:

https://www.patreon.com/Inzaniak

Do you want a custom LoRA or picture? Check out my commission page:

LoRA and Picture Commissions

If you want to support my work for free, you can also check out my music/art here:

  • Bandcamp

  • DeviantArt

  • Patreon
